To compile this app, make sure you installed the Qt4 SDK,
then just run

$ cd bp-nfoview
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

To install it run (after compiling)

$ sudo make install

or to create a debian binary/source package, run

$ dpkg-buildpackage       # binary package
$ dpkg-buildpackage -S    # source package


Feel also free to contact me,
if you found bugs or you want to make a feature suggestion, I'll try my best then ;)
